com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util
Enum Settings

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<Settings>
      com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.util.Settings
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Settings>
public enum Settings
extends Enum<Settings>

This configuration class accesses all values that are read from a settings file in plain text. The settings file cannot be modified at runtime, so all Settings objects are immutable.

Author:
Florian J. Breunig
